    Unlike ``GtkHeaderBar``, :class:`Adw.HeaderBar` allows to toggle title button
    visibility for each side individually, using the
    :attr:`HeaderBar.show-start-title-buttons` and
    :attr:`HeaderBar.show-end-title-buttons` properties.

