    which holds additional per-child properties. You obtain the
    :class:`ViewStackPage` for a child with :meth:`ViewStack.get_page` and you
    can obtain a :class:`Gtk.SelectionModel` containing all the pages with
    :meth:`ViewStack.get_pages`.

