    :class:`ViewStackPage` objects explicitly, and set the child widget as a
    property on it:

    .. code-block:: xml

          <object class=":class:`Adw.ViewStack`" id="stack">
            <child>
              <object class=":class:`Adw.ViewStackPage`">
                <property name="name">overview</property>
                <property name="title">Overview</property>
                <property name="child">
                  <object class=":class:`Adw.StatusPage`">
                    <property name="title">Welcome!</property>
                  </object>
                </property>
              </object>
            </child>
          </object>

